### Enrichment
3d-force-graph (github.com/vasturiano/3d-force-graph) remains actively maintained. The library now supports incremental loading with array spread operators for live-updating graphs — useful for real-time ingestion visualization. Neo4j published guides on 3D graph visualization with WebGL offering layout algorithm ideas. Consider d3-force library for alternative physics engine options.

